Comment should not precede DOCTYPE

The purpose of <!doctype html> is to ensure standards compliant rendering, avoiding quirks mode, even in older browsers.  To fulfill this purpose, it must be the first item in the file. See https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Quirks_Mode_and_Standards_Mode
